quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Vuga uti: “Emwe bagarariji!"
  109,2,"Jewe sinzosenga ivyo musenga (ibigirwamana)."
  109,3,"Na mwe ntimusenga Imana Imwe Rudende nsenga."
  109,4,"Eka nanje sinsenga uko mwebwe musenga."
  109,5,"Kandi na mwe ntimuzosenga Imana Imwe Rudende Allah nsenga."
  109,6,"Mufise idini ryanyu rero, nanje nkagira idini ryanje ntarota mpindura”."
